TypeMaster! - Boost Your Typing Skills with Every New Tab!
Turn every new tab into an exciting challenge with TypeMaster! This Chrome extension brings a fun and engaging typing game right to your browser, helping you improve your typing speed and accuracy while you surf the web. Whether you're a beginner looking to practice or an expert aiming to beat your high score, TypeMaster offers endless entertainment and learning opportunities.

Key Features:
- Interactive Typing Game: Enjoy a fast-paced typing game every time you open a new tab, designed to sharpen your typing skills and reflexes.

- Progress Tracking: Keep track of your scores and progress over time, and challenge yourself to get faster and more accurate with each session.

- Enhanced Search Experience: Your new tab search will be powered by Microsoft Bing, offering you top-quality search results alongside your gaming experience.

By clicking "Add to Chrome", I agree to install the TypeMaster Chrome extension and set my new tab search to be powered by Bing, as outlined in our Terms of Use and Privacy Policy.
